EB02-EB02-028 normal.name: Portgas.D.Ace - EB02-028 (SP)
EB02-EB02-028 normal.description: [On Play] If your Leader's type includes "Whitebeard Pirates", look at 5 cards from the top of your deck; reveal up to 1 Character card with a cost of 2 and add it to your hand. Then, place the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order and play up to 1 Character card with a cost of 2 from your hand rested.

OP07-OP07-111 normal.name: Lilith - OP07-111 (SP)

[Trigger] If your Leader is [Vegapunk], play this card.

OP07-OP07-118 normal.name: Sabo - OP07-118 (SP)

OP13-OP13-001 normal.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (001)

For every DON!! card rested this way, this Leader or up to 1 of your "Straw Hat Crew" type Characters gains +2000 power during this battle.

OP13-OP13-001 parallel.name: Monkey.D.Luffy (001) (Alternate Art)

OP13-OP13-017 normal.name: Monkey.D.Dragon
